6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to aircraft and airports; creating
the Aircraft and Airports Efficiency Act of 2026;
8 providing for noncodification; and providing an
effective date.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
13 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
14 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Aircraft and
15 Airports Efficiency Act of 2026".
16 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
